xxl.core.indexStructures

Class BPlusTreeBulkLoading

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.indexStructures.BPlusTreeBulkLoading
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HilbertRTreeBulkLoading

    public class BPlusTreeBulkLoading
extends Object
    This class provides functionality to bulk-load a BPlusTree. The tree is created bottom-up.
